OL,3,CBudget 2025: Will Reeves scrap the
OL,4,Ccontroversial two-child benefit cap?
OL,6,FIt is estimated that scrapping the cap
OL,7,Fcould lift 350,000 children out of
OL,8,Fpoverty and reduce the depth of
OL,9,Fpoverty for a further 800,000 children.
OL,11,FAfter months of speculation about
OL,12,Fwhether the government will keep the
OL,13,Fcap, scrap it entirely, or partially
OL,14,Flift it, ITV News met families to hear
OL,15,Fhow the chancellor's decision could
OL,16,Fimpact their lives.
OL,18,FMiles Oscar Snowden is a happy, smiley
OL,19,Ftoddler who lives in Thornaby,
OL,20,FTeesside, with his parents.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/17
