OL,6,FHis father, Christopher Snowden, 40,
OL,7,Fwas working as a delivery driver but
OL,8,Fhad to quit his job last month due to
OL,9,Fhealth issues.
OL,11,FHis mother, Lisa Prosser, 39, is
OL,12,Funable to work due to a long-term
OL,13,Fhealth condition and receives
OL,14,Funiversal credit.
OL,16,FMiles has three older half-brothers,
OL,17,Fso he doesn't qualify for benefits
OL,18,Funder the two-child cap policy. The
OL,19,Ffamily now rely on food banks.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/17
