OL,6,F"It's hard because since I've lost my
OL,7,Fjob, and he's 17 months old, we are
OL,8,Fstruggling financially to be able to
OL,9,Fdo stuff," Mr Snowden said.
OL,11,F"We get the money from universal
OL,12,Fcredit, and we end up with about #20
OL,13,Fat the end of it, and we're having to
OL,14,Frely on the food banks to get through.
OL,15,FIt's food for the cupboards, so we're
OL,16,Fnot starving."
