OL,6,FThe family has been relying on
OL,7,FTeesside GrowBaby, a volunteer-led
OL,8,Fscheme that supports around 120
OL,9,Ffamilies a month experiencing food,
OL,10,Fhygiene, and clothing poverty in the
OL,11,Farea.
OL,13,FLast year, the centre helped around
OL,14,F840 families by providing free access
OL,15,Fto pre-loved clothing and essential
OL,16,Fbaby items, such as prams, cots,
OL,17,Fnappies, and toiletries.
