OL,6,FIt also offers a warm, safe space with
OL,7,Fa hot drink and breakfast for those
OL,8,Fstruggling to put their heating on as
OL,9,Fthe months grow colder.
OL,11,FTerrie-Lea Clinton is another parent
OL,12,Fwho regularly receives help. She has
OL,13,Ffive children who were born between
OL,14,F2017, when the cap was introduced, and
OL,15,F2024, and has older step-children.
OL,17,FShe told ITV News the scrapping of the
OL,18,Ftwo-child benefit cap would "put a
OL,19,Fsecurity net in place" for her family.
