OL,3,CBudget 2025: Will Reeves scrap the
OL,4,Ccontroversial two-child benefit cap?
OL,6,FPressure has been piling on the
OL,7,Fchancellor for the past year, with
OL,8,Fcross-party politicians, including
OL,9,Fsome Labour backbenchers, increasing
OL,10,Ftheir calls for the limit to be
OL,11,Fabolished.
OL,13,FMinisters have previously argued they
OL,14,Fdid not have the financial resources
OL,15,Fto lift the cap and that it was
OL,16,F"unaffordable" to do so.
OL,18,FThis leaves the chancellor with a big
OL,19,Fdecision - who pays if the cap goes?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/17
