OL,3,CBudget 2025: Will Reeves scrap the
OL,4,Ccontroversial two-child benefit cap?
OL,6,FUnsurprisingly, the Conservatives, who
OL,7,Fintroduced the cap in 2017 under then-
OL,8,Fprime minister David Cameron, are
OL,9,Fagainst abolishing the cap.
OL,11,FShadow Chancellor Mel Stride
OL,12,Fpreviously scrapping the two-child cap
OL,13,Fas "irresponsible and unfair".
OL,15,F"If Labour do this, they will be
OL,16,Fhanding out money they simply don't
OL,17,Fhave," he wrote in the Times in
OL,18,FSeptember. "They are borrowing to fund
OL,19,Fwelfare, and that is not sustainable
OL,20,For responsible."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/17
