OL,3,CBudget 2025: Will Reeves scrap the
OL,4,Ccontroversial two-child benefit cap?
OL,6,FThere has been some confusion about
OL,7,FReform UK's position on the policy,
OL,8,Fafter its leader Nigel Farage said in
OL,9,FMay that he supported the idea of it
OL,10,Fbeing scrapped in order to encourage
OL,11,Ffamilies to have more children.
OL,13,FBut in recent months, Farage clarified
OL,14,Fthat the party's policy is that the
OL,15,Fcap should only be lifted for "British
OL,16,Fworking couples".
OL,18,FMeanwhile, the Liberal Democrats and
OL,19,Fthe Green Party oppose the two-child
OL,20,Fcap.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/17
