OL,6,FEstimates vary on how much this would
OL,7,Fcost, with the Resolution Foundation
OL,8,Festimating around #3.5 billion by the
OL,9,Fend of this Parliament in 2029/30,
OL,10,Fwhile the Child Poverty Action Group
OL,11,Fand Joseph Rowntree Foundation have
OL,12,Flower calculations of around #3
OL,13,Fbillion by then.
OL,15,FFormer Prime Minister Gordon Brown,
OL,16,Fwho has been one of the more
OL,17,Finfluential voices urging Reeves to
OL,18,Fact, believes he has a solution.
