OL,6,FSpeaking exclusively to ITV News in
OL,7,FAugust, the former Labour chancellor
OL,8,Fproposed funding measures including an
OL,9,Fonline gambling tax, a levy on
OL,10,Fcommercial banks and a change to gift
OL,11,Faid rules for higher rate taxpayers.
OL,13,FBut the Treasury has raised doubts
OL,14,Fover whether such measures would raise
OL,15,Fthe necessary funds, leaving it
OL,16,Funclear how the government will fund
OL,17,Fthe move.
